{"tid":690384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[經貿大混戰] 歐盟對中國技術轉讓措施訴諸世貿　中國表示遺憾","createTime":"2018-06-04T22:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T10:06:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4ef059dacab5c9b3d3a73293c6687c5a973b93","tid":690384,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:40:59.000Z","msg":"歐盟對中國技術轉讓措施訴諸世貿　中國表示遺憾<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399689-20180603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399689-20180603.htm&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ac1235a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399689-20180603.htm&h=0079c4c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399689-20180603.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟指中國政府有關技術轉讓措施，不符合知識產權協定，將會啟動世界貿易組織爭端解決的機制。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，商務部條約法律司負責人表示，中方對歐方的做法表示遺憾</span>，將根據世貿組織爭端解決程序進行妥善處理。中方已收到歐方提出的磋商請求，中國政府一向高度重視知識產權保護，採取眾多強而有力的措施，保護國內外知識產權權利人的合法權益，取得的成績有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n在知識產權合作方面，中歐雙方建立了知識產權工作組機制。通過這一機制，中歐雙方一直保持著有效溝通，在諸多領域取得積極成果。"},{"pid":"e5ded114c005d9c53f2a84b7564de1d448fa10f2","tid":690384,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42552a703e537402901dd8421876be55c889ccc9","tid":690384,"uid":25787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"遺乜嘢憾吖，咪又係支那或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"a904a01082543a192058683d743513be3bb83ac3","tid":690384,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:39:05.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾<br />\n<br />\n真係出手制裁先再講啦"},{"pid":"e3fa1808556b736767fffdcf6cc21871beb55b5c","tid":690384,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T00:19:12.000Z","msg":